title: (Tues Early Bird) Jordan Davis on Touring With Brooks & Dunn  And His New Song About His Wife + Mailbag: Beer Pong for Kids?!
itunes:title: (Tues Early Bird) Jordan Davis on Touring With Brooks & Dunn  And His New Song About His Wife + Mailbag: Beer Pong for Kids?!
description:
Jordan Davis stops by to talk about his new song “What My World Spins Around”, how “Buy Dirt” changed his career and how awesome it’s been to tour with Brooks and Dunn. In the mailbag, a parent has a question about if it’s okay to let his kids play ‘beer pong’ with water.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
